window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Two centuries after humanity colonized the stars, new dangers emerge. The peaceful inhabitants of the Conclave are threatened by expanding alien powers. Invaders threaten the star cluster, attacking our fringe settlements.&nbsp;</p> <p>Captain Bill Gorman has mysteriously disappeared. His clone, set aside for a dark day like this, awakens and begins to put together the pieces. Whatâ€™s gone wrong out on the frontier? Why are our colonies being attacked by aliens while the Conclave worlds dream of better days? And what happened to the original Captain Gorman?&nbsp;</p> <p>Find out in <i>Star Runner</i>, a thrilling all-new interstellar adventure by B. V. Larson, the king of military science fiction.</p>"; 
